---
Source:
  - Title: For Lovers of God Everywhere
    By: Roger Housden
    ISBN: 9781401923877
Page: 166
By: Marguerite Porete
Title: Thought Is No Longer of Worth to Me
---
Thought is no longer of worth to me,
Nor work, nor speech.
Love draws me so high
(Thought is no longer of worth to me)
With her divine gaze,
That I have no intent.
Thought is no longer of worth to me.
Nor work, nor speech.
